data.description: Welcome home to this lovely two-story nestled on a no outlet street; the street borders Fountain Valley Golf Course. Spacious main level has a gorgeous fireplace and a beautiful view of the undeveloped prairieland beyond the backyard. The kitchen is open to the dining area and has a large island for all kinds of versatility; don't miss the convenient walk-in corner pantry too! The den is set in the front of the house for all the southern sunlight. Upstairs you'll find 4 bedrooms, the owner's suite has its own bathroom, with 2 sinks and a walk-in shower. Continue on to the large walk-in closet for all your storage needs. Down the hall you have the full size laundry room and a full bathroom with tub and shower. The walkout basement is mostly framed and ready for you to finish; plus, it is already plumbed for an additional bathroom! Last, but definitely not least, enjoy the three-stall garage with heater! You'll have plenty of space for vehicles and/or that workshop you've always wanted.
